OL,6,FParents face higher fines for school
OL,7,Fabsences as part of attendance drive,
OL,8,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,9,FStacey Foster reports
OL,11,FParents in England who take their
OL,12,Fchildren out of class without
OL,13,Fpermission will face higher fines as
OL,14,Fpart of a drive to boost school
OL,15,Fattendance following the pandemic.
OL,17,FThe Department for Education (DfE) has
OL,18,Fsaid a fine must be considered if a
OL,19,Fchild misses five days of school for
OL,20,Funauthorised absence.
