OL,3,CParents face higher fines for school
OL,4,Cabsences as part of attendance drive
OL,6,FSchool absence fines currently start
OL,7,Fat #60, rising to #120 if they are not
OL,8,Fpaid within 21 days. But the DfE has
OL,9,Fsaid fines will now start at #80,
OL,10,Frising to #160.
OL,12,FIt comes after nearly 400,000 penalty
OL,13,Fnotices were issued to parents in
OL,14,FEngland in 2022-23 for unauthorised
OL,15,Fschool absences ` which was much
OL,16,Fhigher than pre-pandemic levels.
