OL,6,FNearly nine in ten (89.3%) of the
OL,7,Ffines were for unauthorised holidays
OL,8,Fas families looked to book cheaper
OL,9,Fvacations outside school term times,
OL,10,Faccording to DfE figures released in
OL,11,FDecember.
OL,13,FGovernment guidance is expected to
OL,14,Fclarify when financial penalties for
OL,15,Fschool absences should be used to
OL,16,Fensure councils issue fines
OL,17,Fappropriately.
