OL,4,Cabsences as part of attendance drive
OL,6,FThe DfE has said school absence fines
OL,7,Fwill be brought under a national
OL,8,Fframework to help tackle
OL,9,Finconsistencies in their use across
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FUnder the new measures ` which have
OL,13,Fbeen announced as part of the
OL,14,FGovernment's efforts to try to cut
OL,15,Fdown on the number of children who are
OL,16,Fregularly missing school ` every state
OL,17,Fschool in England will share their
OL,18,Fdaily attendance registers with the
OL,19,FDfE, councils and academy trusts.
