OL,6,FGuidance ` setting out how schools and
OL,7,Flocal authorities must take a "support-
OL,8,Ffirst" approach to help pupils and
OL,9,Ftheir families to tackle barriers to
OL,10,Fattendance ` will be made statutory
OL,11,Ffrom August, the DfE has said.
OL,13,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan
OL,14,Fsaid: "Our fantastic schools and
OL,15,Fteachers unlock children's
OL,16,Fimagination, potential and social
OL,17,Fskills which is why improving
OL,18,Fattendance is my number one priority.
