OL,6,F"Today we are taking that next step to
OL,7,Ffurther boost attendance and I want to
OL,8,Fthank those who are working with us
OL,9,Fincluding teachers and heads.
OL,11,F"Education standards have risen
OL,12,Fsharply across the country, with
OL,13,FOfsted ratings up from 68% to nearly
OL,14,F90% since 2010 ` and pupils'
OL,15,Fperformance is ranked as some of the
OL,16,Fbest globally ` so it has never been
OL,17,Fmore valuable to be in school."
