OL,6,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,7,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, said: "A
OL,8,Fconsistent national framework for
OL,9,Ffines makes sense. Currently there is
OL,10,Fsignificant variation between how and
OL,11,Fwhen local authorities issue fines to
OL,12,Fparents.
OL,26,@oD@cOU
